sequenceDiagram
    participant Source as "flow { } 源"
    participant Map as "map 操作符"
    participant Filter as "filter 操作符"
    participant Collector as "collect { } 终端"

    Collector->>Filter: collect(collector)
    Filter->>Map: collect(filterCollector)
    Map->>Source: collect(mapCollector)

    Note over Source: flow 块开始执行

    Source->>Map: emit(rawValue)
    Map->>Map: transform(rawValue)
    Map->>Filter: emit(mappedValue)
    Filter->>Filter: predicate(mappedValue)
    alt predicate = true
        Filter->>Collector: emit(mappedValue)
        Collector->>Collector: 处理 value
    else predicate = false
        Note over Filter: 值被过滤，不向下传递
    end

    Source->>Map: emit(rawValue2)
    Map->>Map: transform(rawValue2)
    Map->>Filter: emit(mappedValue2)
    Filter->>Collector: emit(mappedValue2)
    Collector->>Collector: 处理 value2

    Note over Source: flow 块结束
    Note over Collector: collect 返回
